title: jensen01's Fallout 4 Textures
description:
jensen01 made several very nice little texture packs on the Fallout 4 Nexus. Then for some reason he deleted his account and all of his uploads. 

Luckily, I downloaded all of his work just before he disappeared, managing to get the newest version of each of these packs. They are all in 2k resolution and are much nicer than the default textures.

I will be seeding this indefinitely until jensen01 returns to the Nexus and re-uploads these great textures
